title: NFL ATL: Week 11 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 11 recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling recap all of the Week 11 action including the “Sunday Night Football” matchup between the Kansas City Chiefs and the Denver Broncos. Don’t miss the key takeaways and analysis from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
